that cascade to cartservice.\n\n3. **Cascading Effects**: The latency issues propagate from Redis → cartservice → checkoutservice → frontend, following the system topology.\n\n4. **No Error Status Codes**: The anomaly appears to be primarily performance-related (high latency) rather than error-based, as no status combinations were reported.\n\nThe root cause appears to be Redis performance degradation, which then cascades through cartservice to checkoutservice and ultimately affects the entire checkout flow.", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对监控数据的全面扫描分析，我发现了多个显著的异常指标。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"io_util\", \"node_filesystem_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"rrt\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio和error_ratio出现显著异常，p99变化率达到2.0，表明该服务实例出现严重错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio和error_ratio的p99从0.0飙升到14.05，变化率200%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-06\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_filesystem_usage_rate出现严重异常，文件系统使用率从54.42%飙升到78.23%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_filesystem_usage_rate中位数变化率35.9%，p99变化率31.46%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes和node_memory_usage_rate显示内存资源紧张\",\n      \"evidence\": \"可用内存从9.73GB减少到8.15GB，内存使用率从38.96%上升到48.36%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max出现显著延迟异常，中位数变化率45.73%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从3524ms上升到5613ms，p99从14663.6ms上升到11626.27ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max出现高延迟，中位数变化率27.35%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从3837ms上升到5052.5ms，p99保持在80220.53ms的高位\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"io_util出现异常，可能影响数据库性能\",\n      \"evidence\": \"io_util的p99变化率-20.45%，表明IO使用模式发生变